Requirements
-----------------------------------------------
SilverStripe 2.3.1+
(May work on older versions, has not been tested on any previous to this)


Installation Instructions
-----------------------------------------------
Extract the simplify folder into the top level of your site, and visit
http://www.mysite.com/dev/build?flush=1 to rebuild the database.

Quick start
-----------------------------------------------
1. After installing Simplify, login to the admin interface as a full admin user
2. Click on the Security menu
3. Click on the Group you want to Simplify, or create a new one.
4. Click on the Simplify tab
4. Browse the available tabs and options, and select some you find interesting
5. Save the group and logout
6. Login as one of your users and see the difference!


